info: ●●● ENGLISH: This clinic is offering the Moderna and Johnson & Johnson (Janssen) COVID-19 vaccines which are for people age 18 or older only. The Moderna vaccine requires two doses. La vacuna de Johnson & Johnson requiere de una sola dosis. ●●● PORTUGUÊS: Essa clínica está oferecendo as vacinas da Moderna e da Johnson & Johnson (Janssen) contra a COVID-19, que são para pessoas com 18 anos de idade ou mais. special: If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.
